\ngroups in Peru during its internal armed conflict between 1980 and 2000.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2021 03:24:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 31 Jul 2021 17:34:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-03"}
