ar to those of DNNF. Thus, SAUNF provides the right trade-off in\nknowledge representation for Boolean functional synthesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2021 04:16:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 12:52:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-29"}
