 our model to identify coronal holes from each channel separately and\nshow that the neural network provides the best performance with the combined\nchannel information, but that coronal hole segmentation maps can be also\nobtained solely from line-of-sight magnetograms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2021 12:59:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 May 2021 08:46:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-09"}
