 the style measure. Finally, we\ndemonstrate its efficacy on a large unlabeled public dataset of CAD models.\nSource code and data will be released in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Apr 2021 18:14:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Jul 2021 08:38:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 15:12:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
